Elsie Baker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elsie_Baker 0 Elsie Baker (July 13, 1883 – August 16, 1971) was an American singer and actress. Her career spanned the gamut from vaudeville through silent movies to Victrola to radio to Hollywood and television.
